entries.femaleVariant: Well, that's what you get for a lifetime o' hustlin'.
Nice speech. Remind me not to invite you to my funeral.
How 'bout him? Gonna tell anyone to scrape 'im up and put 'im under?
No one to tell.
'Ey, 'ey, V! Over here, choom!
OK – see that garage, right there? Van's inside. You go in, grab the tech, get out, we split it fifty-fifty. Clear?
OK... Wheels're there...
Hey, Kirk.
I'm not your choom.
[Open]
What the... the fuck's this? Clothes?!
entries.maleVariant: What the... the fuck is this? Clothes?!

entries.femaleVariant: Shit... now a firefight...
Implants. Fuckin' Militech 'ware. I'ma shove these duds right up his ass.
Wow, the fun's just gettin' started. Have a good time, V.
Ugh, fucking fuck...
Oh, look, another gonk. How you like those combat implants, choom? Ha, ha, ha!
Mh, very funny. To you. The fuck's goin' on here?!
entries.maleVariant: Very funny. To you. The fuck is goin' on here?!

entries.femaleVariant: You just crossed a line.
I'm a gonk little bitch.
Your choom, Kirk. Did biz time to time – but see, had this funny feelin' he was tryna play me.
How 'bout a little joke instead? What lies on the ground, pissin' itself an' beggin for mercy?
I'm a gonk little bitch. Happy?
entries.maleVariant: I'm a gonk little bitch. Ya happy?

entries.femaleVariant: 'Sup, Kirk. Happy to see you, too, but how 'bout let's not broadcast it, hm?
Not your choom.
Yeah, sure, just tryna be friendly, is all...
Not chooms, not friends. Biz – now.
Right, right, sorry. No need for a scene.
OK. I'm goin' in.
And you do what?
There any guards?
I want more than fifty.
OK. In I go. Head on a swivel, right?
Thought this was a job for two. Looks like I'm carryin' all the weight here.
All the weight! All the fuckin' weight! Who's gonna keep watch? Me, of course. Anything happens, you'll know.
You scan the area? Anyone inside?
All clear, V. Not a soul. Can waltz right in like you own the place.
No, don't like the split. Two thirds for me, one for you.
entries.maleVariant: Nope, don't like the split. Two thirds for me, one for you.

entries.femaleVariant: You got it.
Know what? Sure. You're all right, V. A pro, a pal. Choom like you's hard to find in this town.
Mhm. Cheap knockoffs, too. Had real great intel, that Kirk... like always, actually.
But hey – could strike out on your own. Open up a stand in Kabuki, or maybe--
All clear, my ass…
Checked out that feelin'. Told 'im I had a transport, preem implants, just sittin' there for the takin'... An' I waited.
See the prank worked.
Yup, sure did. Isn't that right, boys?
Smart girl. Right, chooms – let's delta.
entries.maleVariant: Smart boy. Right, chooms – let's delta.

entries.femaleVariant: What?
You.
I should splatter your brains on the pavement, but I'd just be wasting lead. Only a fuckin' gonk'd run an op with Kirk.
Hey, don't gimme that face. You are what you fuckin' do. So say it – say you're a gonk little bitch and I'll let you live.
